<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over video] </F>
  [Text] Esat Kiratlioglu, deputy leader of the True Path 
Party [TPP], has declared that his party has emerged as the 
leading party from the local elections and the biggest credit 
goes to leader Tansu Ciller. The TPP Chairmanship Council met 
under Kiratlioglu in Ankara and appraised the election results. 
