------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|CDU/CSU with the Greens               |4                                     | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|CDU/CSU with Republikaner             |2                                     | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|SPD with the Greens                   |19                                    | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|SPD with FDP                          |12                                    | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|SPD with Republikaner                 |2                                     | 
